headline: Cook Compression Opens New Service Center in Corpus Christi, Texas
summary: Cook Compression, part of Dover Precision Components and Dover (NYSE: DOV), today announced the opening of a new service center in Corpus Christi, Texas. The facility includes capabilities for the repair, refurbishment and replacement of packing cases, valves, ring and rider bands, pistons and piston rods, cylinders and other related parts.
